\"><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Operator increment&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ã </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;++</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Operator decrement&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Wingdings;\">Ã </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;--</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Contoh :</span></div><pre style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">#include &lt;iostream.h&gt;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">main()<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">{<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int m = 44, n = 66;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&lt;&lt;â€m = â€œ&lt;&lt;m&lt;&lt;â€, n = â€œ&lt;&lt;n&lt;&lt;endl;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;++m; --n;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-fa