&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;n = m++;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&lt;&lt;\"m = \"&lt;&lt;m&lt;&lt;\", n = \"&lt;&lt;n&lt;&lt;endl;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&lt;&lt;\"m = \"&lt;&lt;m++&lt;&lt;endl;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&lt;&lt;\"m = \"&lt;&lt;m&lt;&lt;endl;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cout&lt;&lt;\"m = \"&lt;&lt;++m&lt;&lt;endl;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return 0;<br></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">}</span></span></pre><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Keluarannya :</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">m = 67, n = 67</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">m = 68, n = 67</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">m = 68</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">m = 69</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">m = 70</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Penjelasan :</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Dalam penugasan yang pertama, m adalah pre-increment, menaikkan nilainya menjadi 67, yang selanjutnya dimasukkan ke n.</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Dalam penugasan kedua, m adalah post-increment, sehingga 67 dimasukkan dahulu ke n baru kemudian nilai m-nya dinaikkan, itu sebabnya mengapa nilai m = 68 dan n = 67.</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Dalam penugasan ketiga, m adalah post-increment, sehingga nilai m ( = 68 ) ditampilkan dahulu ( ke layar ) baru kemudian nilai m dinaikkan menjadi 69.</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, 