: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pada contoh diatas, pada saat goto ditemukan maka program akan melompat pernyataan berlabel bawah dan melakukan pernyataan 3.</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">4.6 PERNYATAAN KONDISI ( CONDITIONAL EXPRESSION )</span></b></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pertanyaan Kondisi dibagi menjadi,</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.6.1 Pernyataan&nbsp;<i>if</i></span></b></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; margin-left: 48pt; text-indent: -48pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Digunakan dalam pengambilan keputusan</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; margin-left: 48pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\">Bentuk umum:&nbsp;</span><br></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; margin-left: 84pt; text-indent: 24pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(kondisi) pernyataan1 ;</span></div><div class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; margin-left: 48pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else pernyataan2;</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Pernyataan1 dilaksanakan jika dan hanya jika kondisi yang&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;diinginkan terpenuhi, jika tidak, lakukan pernyataan2.</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Jika anda tidak mempergunakan pernyataan else program tidak akan error, namun jika anda mempergunakan pernyataan&nbsp;<i>else</i>&nbsp;tanpa didahului pernyataan&nbsp;<i>if</i>, maka program akan error.</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Jika pernyataan1 atau pernyataan2 hanya terdiri dari satu baris, maka tanda { } tidak diperlukan, namun jika 