bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pernyataan2a;</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pernyataan2b;</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><img src=\"images/c.jpg\" style=\"width: 326px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px;\">Selain dari if â€¦ else, juga dikenal bentuk if â€¦ else if. Adapun perbedaannya diilustrasikan oleh dua contoh dibawah ini.</span></div><div class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-